# Copy to .env.local (gitignored) and fill in real values.
#
# Google Maps JavaScript API key for the interactive incident map.
# When set, the dashboard map renders with Google Maps; otherwise it
# falls back to the Leaflet/OpenStreetMap layer (no key needed).
#
# IMPORTANT: any key shipped to the browser is publicly visible — lock
# it down in Google Cloud Console:
#   - Application restrictions: HTTP referrers (your dev origin + the
#     deployed Worker URL)
#   - API restrictions: Maps JavaScript API only
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=
